times-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Ftajikistan-detains-9-people-over-russian-concert-shooting%2Famp_articleshow%2F108875235.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Ftajikistan-detains-9-people-over-russian-concert-shooting%2Famp_articleshow%2F108875235.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20drove%20BYD's%20Seal%20electric%20car%20and%20Elon%20Musk%20may%20be%20grateful%20you%20can't%20buy%20one%20in%20the%20US%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22BYD%20Seal%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6601b9793f923f7dab00e91f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EBYD%20has%20overtaken%20Tesla%20as%20the%20world's%20biggest%20maker%20of%20electric%20vehicles.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EI%20drove%20a%20Seal%20for%20a%20week%20and%20was%20impressed%20by%20its%20stylish%20design%2C%20features%20and%20crazy%20acceleration.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20Seal%20is%20a%20similar%20price%20to%20Tesla's%20Model%203%20in%20the%20UK%20%E2%80%94%20but%20BYD%20is%20not%20a%20well-known%20make.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20year%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-q4-sales-less-than-china-byd-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBYD%20overtook%20Tesla%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20the%20world's%20biggest%20seller%20of%20electric%20vehicles.%20The%20Chinese%20company%20does%20not%20sell%20cars%20in%20the%20US%20%E2%80%94%20and%20seemingly%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-byd-electric-car-ev-why-not-coming-to-us-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eno%20plans%20to%20do%20so%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20may%20have%20more%20to%20do%20with%20the%20tariffs%20imposed%20on%20Chinese%20imports%20than%20a%20lack%20of%20desire%20to%20enter%20the%20world's%20second-biggest%20auto%20market%20%E2%80%94%20even%20if%20it%20is%20half%20the%20size%20of%20China%20(where%20about%2030%20million%20vehicles%20were%20sold%20in%202023).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20three%20BYD%20models%20are%20available%20in%20the%20UK.%20The%20smallest%20is%20the%20Dolphin%2C%20a%20similar%20size%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvw-volkswagen-history-nazi-germany-logo-elon-musk-electric-vehicle-2022-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVolkswagen%3C%2Fa%3E%20I-3.%20It's%20followed%20by%20the%20Atto%203%2C%20a%20compact%20SUV%3B%20and%20finally%20the%20Seal%2C%20a%20striking%20four-door%20sedan%20that's%20the%20most%20expensive%20of%20the%20trio%20at%20about%20%C2%A345%2C700%2C%20or%20%2457%2C500.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20borrowed%20a%20BYD%20Seal%20in%20Excellence%20trim%2C%20which%20also%20boasts%20all-wheel%20drive%2C%20for%20a%20week.%20I%20managed%20to%20get%20out%20of%20London%20on%20a%20rainy%20Sunday%20to%20put%20the%20car%20through%20its%20paces.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EVery%20stylish%20indeed%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22BYD%20Seal%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6601b9d216bde8d4ead1db53%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI'd%20barely%20made%20it%20a%20mile%20up%20the%20road%20from%20my%20house%20in%20South%20London%20when%20a%20driver%20in%20a%20Porsche%20SUV%20pulled%20up%20alongside%20me%20and%20started%20gesticulating%20wildly.%20He%20asked%20what%20I%20was%20driving%2C%20and%20I%20explained%20it%20was%20a%20BYD.%20It%20was%20clear%20he%20hadn't%20heard%20of%20the%20make%2C%20which%20is%20no%20great%20surprise%20as%20neither%20had%20any%20of%20my%20friends%2C%20but%20the%20Porsche%20driver%20declared%20it%20striking%20nevertheless.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20lack%20of%20cache%20could%20be%20a%20bit%20of%20an%20issue%20given%20the%20fanciest%20Seal%20is%20priced%20between%20the%20base%20version%20of%20the%20Model%203%20(about%20%C2%A340%2C000%2C%20or%20%2450%2C000%20with%20a%20318-mile%20range%20per%20Tesla's%20website)%20and%20the%20long-range%20version%20that's%20about%20%C2%A350%2C000%20(%2462%2C200%20with%20a%20390-mile%20range.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERange%20rover%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22BYD%20Seal%20screen%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6601c3b93f923f7dab00f3a9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBYD%20says%20the%20Excellence%20has%20a%20maximum%20range%20of%20372%20miles%20and%20when%20the%20car%20was%20delivered%20to%20me%20it%20had%2084%25%20on%20the%20clock%20with%20a%20range%20of%20272%20miles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20time%20I%20got%20to%20Bognor%20Regis%2C%20just%20a%20few%20miles%20along%20the%20coast%20past%20Brighton%20about%20two-and-a-half%20hours%20later%2C%20I%20had%2056%25%20charge%20and%20180%20miles%20of%20range%20left.%20No%20anxiety%20whatsoever%20%E2%80%94%20unlike%20my%20neighbors%20who%20recently%20leased%20an%20electric%20Mini%20that%20has%20a%20range%20of%20about%20120%20miles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EClever%20touches%20galore%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22BYD%20Seal%20interior%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6601cbc53f923f7dab00f7a0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Seal%20has%20upmarket%20touches%20like%20leather%20trim%2C%20and%20a%20plethora%20of%20clever%20features%20such%20as%20a%20driver's%20seat%20that%20goes%20back%20a%20few%20inches%20automatically%20when%20you%20open%20the%20door.%20Even%20so%20it's%20not%20very%20far%20off%20the%20ground%2C%20so%20climbing%20can%20be%20a%20minor%20contortion%20act.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20also%20the%20first%20car%20I've%20driven%20that%20has%20a%20heads-up%20display.%20It%20means%20you%20don't%20have%20to%20take%20your%20eyes%20off%20the%20road%20to%20monitor%20your%20speed%2C%20but%20can%20also%20be%20quite%20distracting%20until%20you%20get%20used%20to%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReading%20the%20spec%20sheet%20I%20see%20there%20are%20features%20I%20failed%20to%20discover%2C%20such%20as%20intelligent%20voice%20control.%20But%20one%20thing%20I%20did%20notice%20was%20the%20way%20the%20door%20handles%20pop%20out%20when%20you%20unlock%20the%20car%2C%20and%20then%20retract.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EHideaway%20handles%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222476%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22BYD%20Seal%20door%20handles%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6603fbdc3f923f7dab01932d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221857%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EReading%20the%20spec%20sheet%20I%20see%20there%20are%20features%20I%20failed%20to%20discover%2C%20such%20as%20intelligent%20voice%20control.%20But%20one%20thing%20I%20did%20notice%20was%20the%20way%20the%20door%20handles%20pop%20out%20when%20you%20unlock%20the%20car%2C%20and%20then%20retract.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBeep%20beep%20beep...%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22BYD%20dashboard%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6601cea73f923f7dab00fab5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Seal%20has%20built-in%204G%20connectivity%20and%20is%20clever%20enough%20to%20tell%20you%20the%20speed%20limit%20on%20the%20screen%20behind%20the%20steering%20wheel%20and%20the%20heads-up%20display.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20another%20clever%20touch%20I%20quickly%20found%20incredibly%20annoying%20was%20the%20insistence%20on%20bleeping%20whenever%20I%20exceeded%20the%20speed%20limit%20by%20a%20mere%20two%20miles%20an%20hour.%20London%20now%20has%20a%2020%20mph%20limit%2C%20meaning%20the%20car%20was%20delivering%20its%20four-stage%20scolding%20over%20and%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20eventually%20delved%20into%20the%20settings%20to%20turn%20the%20function%20off%2C%20but%20of%20course%20it%20turned%20itself%20on%20again%20after%20a%20certain%20period%20had%20elapsed.%20I%20can%20understand%20why%2C%20but%20it%20really%20did%20detract%20from%20the%20Seal's%20many%20pleasures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20thing%20I%20liked%20the%20most%20about%20it%20was%20the%20insane%20acceleration.%20This%20is%20also%20true%20of%20other%20EVs%20like%20Tesla%2C%20but%20it's%20the%20first%20time%20I've%20been%20able%20to%20channel%20my%20inner%20boy%20racer%20and%20leave%20everything%20else%20in%20the%20rear-view%20mirror%20by%20zooming%20away%20when%20traffic%20lights%20turn%20green.%20It's%20hard%20to%20convey%20just%20how%20quickly%20this%20car%20can%20hit%2062%20miles%20(100%20kilometers)%20an%20hour%20%E2%80%94%20officially%20its%203.8%20seconds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeing%20a%20good%20law-abiding%20BI%20writer%20I%20didn't%20exceed%20the%20freeway%20limit%20of%2070%20miles%20an%20hour%20(well%2C%20not%20by%20too%20much%20anyway)%2C%20but%20100%20%E2%80%94%20or%20more%20%E2%80%94%20would've%20been%20no%20problem%20whatsoever.%20The%20all-wheel-drive%20Seal%20sticks%20to%20the%20road%20like%20a%20Ferrari%20(yes%2C%20I%20have%20driven%20one%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0twice%20in%20fact)%2C%20and%20BYD%20boasts%20that%20the%20battery%20is%20integrated%20into%20the%20body%20for%20improved%20rigidity.%20I%20believe%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EPlenty%20of%20room%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22BYD%20Seal%20back%20seat%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6601d2a41caec1275a6931f7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20back%20seat%20has%20ample%20room%20for%20two%20adults%2C%20or%20three%20at%20a%20pinch%20%E2%80%94%20and%20there%20are%20screens%20for%20them%20to%20connect%20devices%20to%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%2012-speaker%20sound%20system%20is%20superb%20and%20I%20very%20much%20enjoyed%20the%20soundtrack%20to%20my%20journey%2C%20which%20included%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdrake-accused-sampling-without-permission-pet-shop-boys-rye-rye-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPet%20Shop%20Boys%3C%2Fa%3E'%20seminal%201990%20album%20%26quot%3BBehaviour%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftaylor-swift-net-worth-spending-2018-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETaylor%20Swift%3C%2Fa%3E's%20%26quot%3BMidnights%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20very%20fun%20%26quot%3BLast%20Man%20Dancing%26quot%3B%20from%20former%20Scissor%20Sisters%20frontman%20Jake%20Shears%20%E2%80%94%20all%20streamed%20from%20Spotify%20on%20my%20iPhone.%20(The%20car%20has%20both%20Apple%20Car%20Play%20and%20Android%20Auto.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAmple%20trunk%20space%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22BYD%20Seal%20trunk%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6601d3271caec1275a6932b8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20room%20in%20the%20trunk%20for%20quite%20a%20lot%20of%20luggage%20%E2%80%94%20and%20there's%20bonus%20storage%20under%20the%20hood%20to%20boot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20entire%20roof%20is%20glass%20and%20mightily%20impressive%2C%20though%20does%20pose%20the%20possibility%20of%20getting%20sunburnt%20perhaps.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EPlug%20it%20in%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225832%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22BYD%20Seal%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F660401701caec1275a69cc45%3Fformat