king%20with%20her%20in%202009%2C%20as%20her%20director%20of%20digital%20strategy%20and%20new%20media.%20During%20that%20time%2C%20I%20shifted%20my%20focus%20toward%20helping%20Beyonc%C3%A9%20bring%20her%20fan%20base%20online.%20This%20is%20when%20I%20learned%20my%20biggest%20marketing%20lessons%20from%20her.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShe's%20the%20most%20gracious%20and%20kind%20person%20I've%20ever%20met.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20she%20knew%20what%20she%20wanted%20from%20her%20team.%20She%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-beyonce-wearing-hat-designed-affected-etsy-business-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehas%20high%20standards%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20for%20those%20around%20her%20because%20she%20has%20high%20standards%20for%20herself.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHere%20are%20three%20big%20takeaways%20from%20working%20with%20Beyonc%C3%A9%20that%20have%20helped%20shape%20my%20career.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%3E1.%20Don't%20build%20community%2C%20facilitate%20it%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPart%20of%20my%20job%20in%20overseeing%20Beyonc%C3%A9's%20digital%20strategy%20was%20maintaining%20her%20Facebook%20page%20and%20Twitter%20account.%20The%20team%20would%20put%20together%20our%20recommendations%2C%20and%20we'd%20present%20these%20ideas%20to%20her%20father%2C%20Matthew%20Knowles%2C%20who%20was%20overseeing%20Music%20World%20Entertainment%2C%20which%20produced%20her%20earlier%20work.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20he%20liked%20our%20ideas%2C%20we'd%20share%20them%20with%20Beyonc%C3%A9.%20She'd%20hear%20us%20out%2C%20say%20what%20she%20liked%20or%20didn't%20like%2C%20and%20give%20recommendations.%20Even%20when%20she%20disagreed%2C%20she%20was%20always%20gracious.%20It%20was%20during%20these%20in-person%20meetings%20that%20it%20seemed%20she%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vanityfair.com%2Fstyle%2F2016%2F09%2Fbeyonce-social-media-instagram-studies%23%3A~%3Atext%3DBeyonc%25C3%25A9%2520doesn%2527t%2520seem%2520too%2Coccasions%252C%2520or%2520to%2520disseminate%2520information.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%20wasn't%20really%20excited%20by%20social%20media%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20or%20inclined%20to%20post%20on%20Facebook%20or%20Twitter.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20was%20back%20in%202009%20or%202010.%20The%20internet%20felt%20like%20the%20wild%2C%20wild%20west.%20There%20were%20no%20rules.%20Beyonc%C3%A9%20had%20just%20finished%20the%20Brazilian%20leg%20of%20her%20%26quot%3BI%20Am%20Sasha%20Fierce%26quot%3B%20tour%2C%20and%20it%20seemed%20like%20social%20media%20wasn't%20for%20her.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20fact%2C%20for%20years%2C%20she%20had%20a%20Twitter%20handle%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-doesnt-beyonc-use-twitter-2016-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eshe%20never%20tweeted%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%3Cspan%3E.%20And%20yet%2C%20she%20had%20lots%20of%20followers%20waiting%20for%20her.%20So%2C%20when%20we%20became%20active%20on%20these%20platforms%20for%20her%2C%20we%20expected%20them%20to%20light%20up%20with%20activity.%20But%20they%20didn't%20in%20proportion%20to%20her%20stardom%2C%20which%20was%20a%20quagmire%20for%20us.%20We%20kept%20asking%20ourselves%3A%20%26quot%3BWhat%20is%20going%20on%20here%3F%20Why%20aren't%20any%20of%20her%20platforms%20taking%20off%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThen%2C%20the%20team%20noticed%20there%20was%20already%20a%20group%20that%20found%20each%20other%20online%2C%20and%20they%20were%20far%20more%20active%20than%20anything%20we%20were%20trying%20to%20do.%20And%20those%20folks%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbeyonce-16-carriages-act-ii-beginning-pandemic-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ewere%20the%2