aled%20in.%20She%20was%20very%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finvest-time-vision-statement-business-owner-entrepreneur2019-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eaware%20of%20her%20creative%20vision%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20I%20never%20had%20one%20bad%20interaction%20with%20her.%20I%20learned%20that%20you%20have%20to%20have%20a%20point%20of%20view%20about%20how%20you%20see%20the%20world.%20You%20have%20to%20know%20what%20you%20like%20and%20be%20courageous%20enough%20to%20follow%20it%20even%20if%20it's%20not%20the%20direction%20most%20people%20are%20going%2C%20and%20folks%20may%20not%20seem%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3Eget%20it%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cspan%3Eright%20away.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%3E3.%20Engage%20authentically%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20seems%20somewhat%20obvious%20now%2C%20but%20people%20who%20went%20online%20to%20engage%20with%20each%20other%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finteresting-things-you-didnt-know-about-beyonce-fun-facts%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eabout%20Beyonc%C3%A9%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20didn't%20want%20to%20be%20treated%20like%20consumers.%20It%20felt%20like%20when%20we%20first%20engaged%20with%20them%2C%20they%20told%20us%3A%20%26quot%3BDon't%20talk%20to%20me%20as%20though%20I%20were%20someone%20with%20money%20in%20their%20pocket.%20Talk%20to%20me%20as%20if%20I%20were%20a%20human%20being%20and%20engage%20with%20me%20based%20on%20your%20understanding%20of%20who%20I%20am%20and%20how%20I%20see%20the%20world.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBeyonc%C3%A9's%20fans%20use%20her%20music%20to%20see%20the%20world%20through%20a%20cultural%20lens.%20The%20fans%20liked%20her%20authenticity%20and%20responded%20to%20it.%20But%20bloggers%20at%20the%20time%20took%20great%20license%20in%20throwing%20shade%20and%20jabs%20he