nID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbillionaire-superyachts-luxury-cost-size-status-symbol-2024-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Superyachts%20are%20the%20ultimate%20multimillion-dollar%20status%20symbol%20for%20the%20rich.%20From%20water%20toys%2C%20pizza%20ovens%20and%20massage%20rooms%2C%20here's%20what%20they%20feature.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mberg%40businessinsider.com%20(Madeline%20Berg)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A19%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbillionaire-superyachts-luxury-cost-size-status-symbol-2024-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22BJP%20Must%20Apologise%20To%20Manmohan%20Singh%3A%20Sanjay%20Raut%20On%20Air%20India%20Probe%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EShiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20leader%20Sanjay%20Raut%20has%20asked%20the%20BJP%20to%20apologise%20to%20former%20prime%20minister%20Manmohan%20Singh%20after%20the%20CBI%20filed%20a%20closure%20report%20in%20its%20Air%20India-Indian%20Airlines%20merger%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20has%20filed%20a%20closure%20report%20in%20its%20probe%20into%20the%20alleged%20irregularities%20in%20the%20leasing%20of%20aircraft%20by%20NACIL%2C%20a%20company%20formed%20by%20the%20merger%20of%20Air%20India%20and%20Indian%20Airlines%20during%20the%20UPA%20era%2C%20as%20there%20was%20no%20%26quot%3Bevidence%20of%20any%20wrongdoing%26quot%3B%2C%20officials%20said%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENCP%20leader%20Praful%20Patel%2C%20who%20now%20belongs%20to%20the%20outfit%20headed%20by%20Ajit%20Pawar%2C%20was%20the%20Union%20civil%20aviation%20minister%20in%20the%20earlier%20Congress-led%20United%20Progress%20Alliance%20(UPA)%20government%20when%20the%20leasing%20was%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20to%20reporters%2C%20Raut%20said%20the%20BJP%20had%20made%20a%20hue%20and%20cry%20over%20alleged%20corruption%20in%20the%20civil%20aviation%20sector%20during%20Manmohan%20Singh's%20tenure%20as%