neral%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Telangana%20phone-tapping%20case%20involves%20gathering%20electronic%20data%20not%20just%20for%20political%20intelligence%2C%20but%20to%20blackmail%20leaders%2C%20and%20even%20private%20companies%20and%20Tollywood%20celebrities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20leader%20N%20Uttam%20Kumar%20Reddy%20told%20NDTV%20all%20this%20happened%20with%20the%20knowledge%20of%20the%20leadership%20of%20the%20previous%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%20(BRS)%20government.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20only%20a%20matter%20of%20time%20before%20they%20(BRS)%20leaders%20come%20under%20the%20ambit%20of%20the%20investigation%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Reddy%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20accused%20No.%201%2C%20T%20Prabhakhar%20Rao%2C%20is%20in%20the%20US.%20Sources%20said%20investigators%20expect%20him%20to%20make%20himself%20available%20soon%20to%20join%20the%20probe.%20A%20'lookout%20circular'%20to%20catch%20wanted%20people%20at%20entry%20and%20exit%20points%20such%20as%20airports%20has%20also%20been%20issued%20against%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShravan%20Rao%20-%20also%20believed%20to%20be%20out%20of%20the%20country%20-%20allegedly%20helped%20set%20up%20Israeli-origin%20phone-tapping%20equipment%20and%20servers%20on%20the%20premises%20of%20a%20local%20school.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20other%20Telangana%20police%20officers%20are%20being%20investigated%20in%20connection%20with%20this%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%20others%20-%20Additional%20Superintendents%20of%20Police%20(SP)%20Bhujanga%20Rao%20and%20Thirupathanna%2C%20and%20Deputy%20SP%20Praneeth%20Rao%20-%20have%20already%20been%20arrested.%20The%20police%20said%20Bhujanga%20Rao%20and%20Thirupathanna%2C%20arrested%20last%20week%2C%20had%20admitted%20to%20monitoring%20private%20individuals%20illegally%20and%20destroying%20the%20evidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20list%20of%20individuals%20whose%20devices%20were%20reportedly%20monitored%20include%20Chief%20Minister%20Revanth%20Reddy%2C%20and%20members