0with%20CPIM%20also%20contesting%20one%20seat.%20This%20announcement%20followed%20the%20Congress%20relinquishing%20its%20stake%20in%20the%20Purnea%20Lok%20Sabha%20constituency.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20NEWS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Hair%20Straightening%20Turns%20Into%20Nightmare%20After%20Woman%20Suffers%20Kidney%20Damage%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20woman%20suffered%20kidney%20damage%20after%20undergoing%20hair-straightening%20treatment%20at%20a%20salon.%20The%20case%20has%20been%20published%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nejm.org%2Fdoi%2Ffull%2F10.1056%2FNEJMc2400528%5C%22%3EThe%20New%20England%20Journal%20of%20Medicine%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20which%20doctors%20have%20described%20what%20happened%20to%20the%20woman.%20Her%20identity%20has%20been%20kept%20secret%20in%20the%20study.%20One%20of%20the%20doctors%20who%20treated%20her%20said%20one%20of%20the%20products%20used%20for%20hair%20straightening%20likely%20caused%20organ%20injuries.%20The%20doctor%20also%20said%20that%20the%2026-year-old%20woman%20visited%20the%20salon%20to%20receive%20the%20popular%20hair%20treatment%20in%20June%202020%2C%20April%202021%20and%20July%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20woman%20had%20no%20previous%20health%20issues%2C%20but%20after%20each%20visit%2C%20she%20experienced%20vomiting%2C%20diarrhoea%2C%20fever%20and%20back%20pain.%20She%20also%20reported%20burning%20sensation%20on%20her%20scalp%20during%20the%20treatment%20and%20developed%20ulcers%20on%20her%20head%2C%20the%20study%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20doctors%20noticed%20kidney%20malfunction%20after%20finding%20raised%20levels%20of%20creatinine%20in%20her%20blood.%20She%20had%20blood%20in%20her%20urine%20after%20which%20the%20doctors%20asked%20the%20woman%20to%20undergo%20a%20CT%20scan%2C%20but%20it%20showed%20no%20other%20sign%20of%20infection%20and%20her%20kidneys%20too%20were%20not%20blocked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20woman%20told%20the%20doctors%20that%20her%20hair%20was%20treated%20with%20a%20straightening%20cream%20containing%20the%20chemical%20glyoxylic%20acid.%20The%20doctors%20arrived%20at%20the%20conclusion%20that%20this%20likely%20caused%20her%20scalp%20to%20burn%20and%20ulcerate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20experiments%20on%20mice%2C%20they%20theorised%20that%20the%20acid%20absorbed%20through%20her%20skin%20and%20reached%20her%20kidneys%2C%20which%20caused%20damage%20upon%20being%20broken%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20study%20said%20the%20woman%20suffered%20recurrent%20episodes%20of%20acute%20kidney%20injury%20due%20to%20oxalate%20nephropathy%2C%20a%20rare%20disorder%20that%20causes%20kidney%20function%20to%20decrease%20due%20to%20the%20build-up%20of%20calcium%20oxalate%20crystals%20in%20kidney%20tubules.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20added%20that%20the%20hair-straightening%20procedures%20provide%20evidence%20that%20glyoxylic%20acid%20is%20responsible.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20would%20seem%20wise%20to%20ban%20the%20use%20of%20glyoxylic%20acid%20in%20these%20products%20and%20request%20that%20manufacturers%20find%20another%2C%20safer%20compound%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr%20Joshua%20David%20King%2C%20an%20associate%20professor%20of%20medicine%20and%20pharmacy%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Maryland%2C%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livescience.com%2Fhealth%2Fviruses-infections-disease%2Fhair-straightening-cream-tied-to-womans-repeated-kidney-damage%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ELive%20Science%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHair%20straightening%20is%20a%20hair%20styling%20technique%20used%20since%20the%201890s%20involving%20the%20flattening%20and%20straightening%20of%20hair%20in%20order%20to%20give%20it%20a%20smooth%2C%20streamlined%20and%20sleek%20appearance.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711699320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fmdqa2pig_hair-straightening-unsplash-1200_625x300_29_March_24.jpg%22%2