a%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.macrumors.com%2F2024%2F03%2F28%2Fapple-sues-former-employee-for-alleged-leaking%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMacRumors%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EApple%20said%20it%20discovered%20the%20leaks%20in%20late%202023.%20When%20confronted%2C%20it%20said%20Aude%20denied%20his%20involvement%20but%20then%20feigned%20a%20bathroom%20break%20and%20%26quot%3Bpermanently%20deleted%20significant%20amounts%20of%20evidence%20from%20his%20device.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20included%20deleting%20the%20Signal%20app%20%E2%80%94%20which%20he%20used%20for%20communications%20%E2%80%94%20from%20his%20work-issued%20phone%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20lawsuit%20said%20that%20Aude%20often%20saved%20screenshots%20of%20his%20communications%20on%20his%20work%20iPhone%20%26quot%3Bto%20preserve%20them%20for%20posterity%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20Apple%20was%20able%20to%20retrieve%20those.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Apple's%20lawsuit%2C%20an%20analysis%20of%20Aude's%20Apple-issued%20work%20iPhone%20showed%20he%20had%20over%201%2C400%20encrypted%20communications%20with%20one%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%20journalist%20over%20a%20four-month%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAude%20also%20sent%20a%20journalist%20at%20The%20Information%20over%2010%2C000%20text%20messages%2C%20and%20traveled%20to%20meet%20her%2C%20according%20to%20Apple.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAude's%20screenshots%20were%20attached%20to%20the%20lawsuit.%20In%20one%20particular%20leak%20to%20the%20Journal%20journalist%20around%20April%202023%2C%20Aude's%20screenshots%20showed%20%26quot%3B'giddy%20anticipation%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Bchaos%26quot%3B%20awaiting%20the%20company%20following%20the%20publication%20of%20leaked%20information%2C%20Apple%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAude%20had%20also%20characterized%20the%20leak%20to%20other%20colleagues%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bnecessary%20evil%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20connection%20with%20one%20leak%2C%20Mr.%20Aude%20admitted%20that%20he%20violated%20his%20obligations%20to%20Apple%20so%20he%20could%20'kill'%20products%20and%20features%20with%20which%20he%20took%20issue%2C%26quot%3B%20Apple%20said%20separately%20in%20the%20lawsuit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAude's%20leaking%20of%20information%20led%20to%20the%20publication%20of%20multiple%20news%20reports%2C%20according%20to%20Apple.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHis%20disclosures%20also%20have%20impeded%20Apple's%20ability%20to%20surprise%20and%20delight%20with%20its%20new%20offerings%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20tech%20company%20said%20in%20its%20lawsuit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Aude's%20employment%20has%20been%20terminated%2C%20Apple%20said%20he%20poses%20an%20%26quot%3Bongoing%20threat%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20company%20due%20to%20his%20knowledge%20of%20its%20confidential%20and%20proprietary%20information%2C%20as%20well%20as%20his%20%26quot%3Blong%20and%20extensive%20history%20of%20disclosing%20it%20to%20third%20parties%20intentionally%20and%20without%20authorization.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EApple%20is%20pursuing%20a%20jury%20trial%2C%20damages%2C%20and%20an%20order%20directing%20Aude%20not%20to%20disclose%20the%20company's%20confidential%20and%20proprietary%20information%20to%20third%20parties%20without%20its%20consent.%20It%20also%20wants%20Aude%20to%20give%20up%20his%20discretionary%20bonuses%20and%20restricted%20stock%20units.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EApple%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%2C%20sent%20outside%20business%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-sues-former-employee-andrew-aude-product-leak-work-iphone-2024-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711697661000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F660624863f923f7dab0277cd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-sues-former-employee-andrew-aude-product-leak-work-iphone-20