Cp%3EHitting%20back%2C%20Delhi%20Health%20Minister%20Saurabh%20Bharadwaj%20on%20Thursday%20said%20VK%20Saxena%20had%20taken%20action%20against%20officers%20earlier%20too%20without%20consulting%20the%20chief%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20note%20to%20LG%20on%20March%2020%2C%20Saurabh%20Bharadwaj%20had%20demanded%20the%20immediate%20removal%20of%20the%20principal%20of%20the%20state-run%20medical%20college%2C%20alleging%20that%20he%20was%20uncooperative%20with%20the%20victims%20and%20that%20he%20discouraged%2Fdemotivated%20them%20from%20pursuing%20the%20case%20further.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Saxena%20has%20already%20directed%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20to%20expedite%20criminal%20proceedings%20and%20also%20directed%20the%20chief%20secretary%20to%20expedite%20disciplinary%20proceedings%20in%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20find%20it%20pertinent%20to%20highlight%20that%20the%20Hon'ble%20Health%20Minister%2C%20in%20both%20the%20current%20note%20and%20a%20previous%20correspondence%20to%20the%20Chief%20Secretary%2C%20has%20requested%20the%20immediate%20transfer%20of%20the%20incumbent%20principal%20and%20the%20Head%20of%20the%20Department%20of%20Pharmacology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20irony%20lies%20in%20the%20fact%20that%20although%20the%20Hon'ble%20Health%20Minister%20has%20made%20a%20request%20for%20the%20transfer%20of%20the%20Principal%20of%20...%20the%20file%20for%20his%20transfer%20has%20been%20held%20up%20by%20you%2C%20as%20the%20chairman%20of%20NCCSA%2C%20since%20February%2014%2C%202024.%20Despite%20reminders%20from%20the%20Member%20Secretary%20of%20NCCSA%2C%20the%20proposal%20is%20still%20pending%20for%20your%20recommendations%20on%20the%20matter%2C%26quot%3B%20read%20LG's%20note.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kejriwal%20is%20the%20chairman%20of%20NCCSA.%20He%20was%20arrested%20on%20March%2021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaurabh%20Bharadwaj%20on%20Thursday%20said%20that%20the%20file%20Mr%20Saxena%20is%20talking%20about%20pertains%20to%20transfer%20of%2017%20medical%20directors%20and%20medical%20superintendent%20of%20different%20hospitals%20and%20the%20name%20of%20the%20principal%20was%20among%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20a%20routine%20file.%20There%20was%20no%20mention%20of%20the%20sexual%20harassment%20case%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20January%2031%2C%20a%20professor%20at%20the%20medical%20college%20made%20%26quot%3Bobscene%26quot%3B%20remarks%20to%20two%20MBBS%20students%20and%20tried%20to%20inappropriately%20touch%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20aggrieved%20students%20filed%20their%20complaints%20at%20the%20principal's%20office%20on%20February%201.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20lodging%20the%20complaint%2C%20the%20students%20had%20hoped%20that%20perhaps%20some%20action%20would%20be%20taken%20in%20this%20matter.%20This%20case%20was%20also%20referred%20to%20the%20Internal%20Complaints%20Committee%20(ICC)%2C%20but%20days%20passed%20and%20no%20action%20was%20taken%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20Instead%20of%20taking%20action%2C%20the%20principal%20and%20other%20hospital%20officials%20exerted%20pressure%20on%20the%20students%20to%20withdraw%20their%20complaints%2C%20he%20charged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20students%20then%20approached%20police%20and%20FIRs%20were%20registered%20on%20February%2022.%20%26quot%3BI%20learned%20about%20this%20case%20through%20social%20media%20on%20March%2018.%20I%20immediately%20called%20those%20two%20students%20for%20a%20meeting.%20They%2C%20along%20with%20their%20seniors%20and%20a%20warden%2C%20came%20to%20my%20office%20and%20explained%20the%20whole%20incident%20in%20detail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20listening%20to%20the%20students%2C%20when%20I%20spoke%20to%20the%20principal%20of%20the%20medical%20college%2C%20he%20seemed%20to%20protect%20the%20guilty%20professor%20and%20instead%20started%20accusing%20the%20students%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Bharadwaj%20said%20he%20wrote%20a%20letter%20to%20the%20chief%20secretary%20the%20same%20day%2C%20asking%20why%20he%20had%20not%20received%20the%20report%20of%20the%20ICC%2C%20formed%20in%20early%20February%2C%20in%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaurabh%20Bharadwaj%20said%20a%20doctor%20or%20any%20other%20health%20officer%20or%20employee%20is%20transferred%20from%20one%20place%20to%20another%20using%20the%20%26quot%3Bdetailment%26quot%3B%20procedure%2C%20and%20there%20is%20no%20need%20for%20NCCSA%20approval%20for%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20that%20the%20health%20secretary%20has%20the%20power%20to%20use%20his%20power%20to%20transfer%20any%20officer%20or%20employee%20of%20the%20health%20department%20from%20one%20hospital%20to%20another.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20also%20wrote%20to%20the%20LG%20that%20when%20the%20police%20can%20complete%20their%20report%20within%20so%20many%20days%2C%20then%20why%20is%20the%20ICC%20taking%20so%20long%20to%20complete%20its%20investigation%20report%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaurabh%20Bharadwaj%20said%20he%20has%20learnt%20that%20the%20ICC%20had%20given%20a%20clean%20chit%20to%20the%20accused.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20urge%20the%20LG%20that%20the%20health%20secretary%20has%20the%20authority%2C%20you%20can%20immediately%20detail%20those%20guilty%20officials.%20I%20request%20you%20to%20take%20immediate%20action%20against%20these%20guilty%20officials%20and%20detail%20them%20as%20soon%20as%20possible%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711694280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2F14qqmfk8_arvind-kejriwal-news-in-hindi-_625x300_21_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsex-harassment-file-stuck-due-to-arvind-kejriwals-inaction-lt-governor-5329790%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Since%20February%2014%2C%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20has%20been%20sitting%20on%20the%20file%20that%20recommended%20the%20removal%20o