%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-debt-borrowers-apply-income-driven-repayment-save-plan-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBiden's%20SAVE%20income-driven%20repayment%20plan%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20implemented%20over%20the%20summer%20to%20give%20borrowers%20cheaper%20monthly%20payments%20with%20a%20shorter%20timeline%20for%20relief.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lawsuit%2C%20filed%20in%20Kansas'%20district%20court%20against%20Biden%20and%20Education%20Secretary%20Miguel%20Cardona%2C%20stated%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Blawsuit%20is%20now%20necessary%20to%20prevent%20Defendants%20from%20continuing%20to%20flout%20the%20law%2C%20which%20includes%20ignoring%20Supreme%20Court%20decisions%2C%26quot%3B%20referring%20to%20the%20high%20court's%20decision%20at%20the%20end%20of%20June%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-forgiveness-blocked-supreme-court-strikes-down-debt-cancellation-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estrike%20down%20Biden's%20first%20attempt%20at%20broad%20student-loan%20forgiveness%3C%2Fa%3E%20using%20the%20HEROES%20Act%20of%202003.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOnce%20again%2C%20the%20Biden%20administration%20has%20decided%20to%20steal%20from%20the%20poor%20and%20give%20to%20the%20rich%2C%26quot%3B%20Kobach%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ksnt.com%2Fnews%2Fkansas%2Flive-kobach-talks-biden-administration-lawsuit-on-student-loan-forgiveness%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20during%20a%20Thursday%20press%20conference.%20%26quot%3BHe%20is%20forcing%20people%20who%20did%20not%20go%20to%20college%2C%20or%20who%20worked%20their%20way%20through%20college%2C%20to%20pay%20for%20the%20loans%20of%20those%20who%20ran%20up%20exorbitant%20student%20debt.%20This%20coalition%20of%20Republican%20attorneys%20general%20will%20stand%20in%20the%20gap%20and%20stop%20Biden.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20the%20Education%20Department%20implemented%20a%20provision%20of%20the%20SAVE%20plan%20