0the%20company%20desperately%20needs%20to%20generate%20more%20revenue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20cancellations%20also%20represent%20a%20drag%20on%20company%20costs.%20While%20it%20costs%20%24250%20to%20reserve%20a%20Fisker%2C%20that%20amount%20is%20refundable%20aside%20from%20a%20%2425%20processing%20fee%2C%20the%20company's%20website%20says.%20Individuals%20who%20reserve%20more%20than%20one%20of%20the%20company's%20EVs%20are%20entitled%20to%20a%20%24100%20refund%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eif%20they%20cancel%2C%20according%20to%20Fisker's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fiskerinc.com%2Flegal%2Freservation-terms%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereservation%20terms%20online%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20company%20said%20a%20reservation%20%26quot%3Bwill%20hold%20your%20approximate%20spot%20in%20our%20order%20queue%20to%20purchase%20your%20Fisker%20EV.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20clear%20how%20many%20reservation%20cancellations%20Fisker%20has%20already%20reimbursed%20in%20the%20years%20since%20November%202019%2C%20when%20it%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.prnewswire.com%2Fnews-releases%2Ffisker-ocean-reservations-open-convenient-mobile-app-affordable-pricing-and-all-digital-experience-unveiled-300965984.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebegan%20accepting%20reservations%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20the%20total%20cost%20to%20date%20of%20around%2040%2C000%20reservation%20reimbursements%20would%20be%20in%20the%20ballpark%20of%20%249%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20also%20has%20a%20few%20thousand%20order%20cancellations%2C%20according%20to%20the%20data%20viewed%20by%20BI%2C%20which%20are%20different%20than%20reservations%20and%20not%20fully%20refundable.%20The%20company%20says%20on%20its%20website%20it%20will%20keep%20the%20%245%2C000%20order%20deposit%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20transportation%20fee%20if%20a%20cancellation%20is%20made%20after%20the%20company%20has%20started%20the%20process%20of%20transporting%20the%20vehicle%20to%20the%20custo