n%20March%2022%2C%20Wilson%20wrote%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20wrote%20about%20an%20asshole%20in%20my%20book.%20Now%2C%20said%20asshole%20is%20trying%20to%20threaten%20me.%20He's%20hired%20a%20crisis%20PR%20manager%20and%20lawyers.%20He%20is%20trying%20to%20stop%20press%20coming%20out%20about%20my%20book.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWilson%20said%20the%20book%20would%20come%20out%20regardless%2C%20%26quot%3Band%20you%20will%20all%20know%20the%20truth.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EDays%20later%2C%20Wilson%20finally%20named%20Cohen%20as%20the%20person%20she%20says%20hired%20lawyers%20to%20threaten%20her%20memoir%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20March%2024%2C%20Wilson%20posted%20another%20Instagram%20story%20naming%20Cohen%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Basshole%26quot%3B%20she'd%20written%20about%20in%20%26quot%3BRebel%20Rising.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20will%20not%20be%20bullied%20or%20silenced%20by%20high%20priced%20lawyers%20or%20crisis%20PR%20managers.%20The%20'asshole'%20I%20am%20talking%20about%20in%20ONE%20CHAPTER%20of%20my%20book%20is%3A%20Sacha%20Baron%20Cohen.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20People%20magazine%20published%20an%20excerpt%20from%20Wilson's%20book%20detailing%20her%20claims%20about%20Cohen's%20behavior%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpeople.com%2Frebel-wilson-details-allegations-about-sacha-baron-cohen-he-calls-false-exclusive-8620597%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EPeople%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20published%20an%20excerpt%20from%20%26quot%3BRebel%20Rising%2C%26quot%3B%20in%20which%20Wilson%20alleges%20that%20Cohen%20frequently%20asked%20her%20to%20go%20nude%20in%20%26quot%3BThe%20Brothers%20Grimsby.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20felt%20like%20every%20time%20I'd%20speak%20to%20SBC%2C%20he'd%20mention%20that%20he%20wanted%20me%20to%20go%20naked%20in%20a%20future%20scene.%20I%20was%20like%2C%20'Ha%2C%20I%20don't%20do%20nudity%2C%20Sacha.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWriting%20about%20a%20scene%20in%20the%20film%20shot%20in%20Cape%20Town%2C%20Wilson%20says%3A%20%26quot%3BSBC%20summons%20me%20via%20a%20production%20assistant%20saying%20that%20I'm%20needed%20to%20film%20an%20additional%20scene.%20'Okay%2C%20well%2C%20we're%20gonna%20film%20this%20extra%20scene%2C'%20SBC%20says.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThen%20he%20pulls%20his%20pants%20down%20%E2%80%A6%20SBC%20says%20very%20matter-of-factly%3A%20'Okay%2C%20now%20I%20want%20you%20to%20stick%20your%20finger%20up%20my%20ass.'%20And%20I'm%20like%2C%20'What%3F%3F%20%E2%80%A6%20No!!'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20now%20scared.%20I%20wanted%20to%20get%20out%20of%20there%2C%20so%20I%20finally%20compromised%3A%20I%20slapped%20him%20on%20the%20ass%20and%20improvised%20a%20few%20lines%20as%20the%20character%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20continues.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ECohen's%20representatives%20have%20denied%20Wilson's%20allegations%20and%20provided%20anonymous%20source%20statements%20in%20his%20defense%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20Cohen%20denied%20the%20allegations%20in%20an%20emailed%20statement%20to%20BI%20on%20March%2025%2C%20the%20day%20after%20Wilson%20publicly%20named%20him%20on%20her%20Instagram%20story.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EThey%20wrote%3A%20%26quot%3BWhile%20we%20appreciate%20the%20importance%20of%20speaking%20out%2C%20these%20demonstrably%20false%20claims%20are%20directly%20contradicted%20by%20extensive%20detailed%20evidence%2C%20including%20contemporaneous%20documents%2C%20film%20footage%2C%20and%20eyewitness%20accounts%20from%20those%20present%20before%2C%20during%2C%20and%20after%20the%20production%20of%20'The%20Brothers%20Grimsby.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20March%2028%2C%20Cohen's%20spokesperson%20also%20provided%20BI%20(via%20email)%20with%20nine%20statements%20from%20anonymous%20crew%20members%2C%20producers%2C%20and%20writers%20who%20said%20they%20worked%20with%20Cohen%20and%20Wilson%20on%20%26quot%3BThe%20Brothers%20Grimsby.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C