0of%20concrete%20in%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20slab%20is%20replaced%20by%20filler%20material.%E2%80%9D%20The%20roofs%20also%20have%20clay%20tiles%20on%20the%20roofs%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20used%20red%20soil%2C%20lime%2C%20cow%20dung%2C%20rice%20dusk%2C%20egg%20and%20jaggery%20to%20make%20a%20paste%20for%20construction%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20the%20homestay%20features%20rainwater%20harvesting%2C%20and%20they%20are%20in%20the%20process%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F107005%2Fever-wondered-what-a-homemaker-thinks-of-solar-panels%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einstalling%20solar%20panels%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20harness%20the%20sun.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20also%20make%20compost%20out%20of%20our%20kitchen%20waste%2C%20which%20is%20then%20used%20in%20our%20garden.%20We%20grow%20all%20our%20plants%20and%20food%20organically%20so%20our%20guests%20can%20enjoy%20fresh%20food%20daily.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20place%20boasts%205%20bedrooms%2C%203%20balconies%2C%20and%203%20living%20spaces%20for%20guests%20to%20enjoy.%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20the%20homestay%20is%20shared%20by%20us%20with%20the%20guests%2C%20we%20also%20prioritise%20their%20privacy.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajchandar%20highlights%2C%20%E2%80%9CA%20unique%20feature%20of%20the%20property%20is%20its%20natural%20coolness%20regardless%20of%20the%20weather%20outside.%20With%2050%20upcycled%20windows%20that%20are%20over%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F336315%2Fsnow-in-himachal-homestay-vacation-kathkuni-old-manali-restored-house%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E100%20years%20old%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20plenty%20of%20air%20circulates%20inside.%20Additionally%2C%20since%20the%20house%20is%20made%20of%20mud%20and%20clay%2C%20it%20remains%20naturally%20cool%20throughout%20the%20year.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3