%20you%20tell%20the%20tourists%20about%20these%20plants%3F%E2%80%9D%20she%20asked%20a%20perplexed%20but%20excited%20Hule.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20will%20learn%20everything%20about%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20Hule%20replied.%20She%20was%20excited%20at%20the%20prospect%20of%20knowing%20more%20about%20the%20vegetation%20that%20she%20had%20often%20admired%20herself.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20eager%20to%20know%20about%20their%20uses%2C%20benefits%2C%20how%20they%20helped%20the%20environment%20and%20more.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98Swamini%E2%80%99%20self-help%20group%20that%20comprises%20nine%20women%20and%20one%20man%20in%20the%20Sindhudurg%20district.%20The%20group%20earns%20around%20Rs%202%2C00%2C000%20a%20year%20by%20charging%20every%20tourist%20a%20fare%20of%20Rs%20200%20for%20the%20boating%20trip.%20They%20conduct%20a%20total%20of%20seven%20boating%20trips%20a%20day%20during%20season%20time.%20The%20women%20are%20supported%20by%20the%20staff%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F301797%2Fex-security-guard-prasenjit-mandal-helps-bali-sundarban-foundation-battles-poverty-climate-change%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20Mangrove%20Cell%3C%2Fa%3E%20under%20the%20Maharashtra%20Forest%20Department.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fwomen-empowerment-3-1710768594.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20self%20help%20group%20model%20has%20been%20extremely%20successful%20and%20Rashmi%20has%20helped%20hundreds%20of%20women%20get%20financial%20independence%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fwomen-empowerment-3-1710768594.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebett