C%20Greeneria%20collaborated%20with%20Prayagraj%20Smart%20City%20to%20illuminate%20900%20streetlights%20using%2015%20tonnes%20of%20organic%20waste.%20In%20Dharamshala%20and%20Belagavi%2C%20five%20tonnes%20of%20organic%20waste%20power%20450%20streetlights%20each.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20corporations%20like%20Hewlett%20Packard%2C%20and%20Capgemini%20are%20making%20strides%20in%20waste%20management.%20For%20instance%2C%20in%20Hinjewadi%2C%20Pune%2C%206%2C000%20employees%20from%20Hewlett%20Packard%20generate%20one%20ton%20per%20day%20(TPD)%20of%20waste%2C%20producing%2035%20kg%20of%20gas%2C%20equivalent%20to%20expensive%20LPG.%20%E2%80%9CBy%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F181269%2Fifs-hero-biogas-sustainability-compost-forest-madhya-pradesh%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econverting%20waste%20into%20biogas%20and%20fertiliser%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20these%20companies%20not%20only%20reduce%20LPG%20bills%20but%20also%20obtain%20organic%20fertiliser%20as%20an%20additional%20asset%20for%20their%20large%20campuses%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%202081px)%20100vw%2C%202081px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fimage-039_11zon-1710998721.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222081%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fimage-039_11zon-1710998721.jpg%202081w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fimage-039_11zon-1710998721-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fimage-039_11zon-1710998721-500x375.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fimage-039_11zon-1710998721-768x576.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fimage-039_11zon-1710998721-1536x1152.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fimage-039_11zon-1710998721-2048x1536.jpg%202048w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fimage-039_11zon-1710998721-150x113.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-345428%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221561%5C%22%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20over%20277%20installations%20across%20the%20country%2C%20Greeneria%20continues%20to%20address%20challenges%20in%20distributing%20biogas%20efficiently.%20Kumar%20suggests%20converting%20biogas%20into%20electricity%20or%20directing%20it%20to%20shared%20spaces%20for%20community%20use%2C%20turning%20waste%20management%20into%20a%20corporate%20social%20responsibility%20initiative.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSunlight%20is%20necessary%20for%20solar%20energy%2C%20and%20wind%20is%20needed%20for%20wind%20energy.%20However%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20always%20a%20lot%20of%20waste%20in%20towns%20and%20villages.%20By%20using%20waste%20for%20biogas%2C%20you%20get%20three%20benefits%20in%20one%20%E2%80%94%20fertiliser%2C%20useful%20gas%2C%20and%20efficient%20waste%20management.%20That%E2%80%99s%20why%20I%20call%20it%20the%20king%20of%20renewable%20energy!%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGreeneria%20is%20a%20testament%20effective%20to%20the%20power%20of%20perseverance%20and%20innovation%20in%20addressing%20pressing%20environmental%20issues.%20The%20company%20is%20not%20only%20contributing%20to%20a%20cleaner%2C%20more%20sustainable%20India%20but%20also%20setting%20an%20example%20for%20businesses%20worldwide%20to%20embrace%20eco-friendly%20practices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Kumar%20aptly%20puts%20it%2C%20%E2%80%9COne%20of%20the%20simplest%20ways%20to%20express%20patriotism%20towards%20India%20is%20by%20segregating%20our%20waste.%20Adopt%20a%20two%20or%20three-bin%20system.%20Use%20one%20bin%20for%20electronic%20waste%20and%20hazardous%20materials%2C%20another%20for%20organic%20waste%20(coloured%20green)%2C%20and%