%20the%20best%20friends%20of%20any%20middle-class%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20use%20it%20for%20everything%20from%20travelling%20in%20the%20city%20to%20buying%20groceries.%20That%20means%20that%20these%20families%20need%20their%20two-wheelers%20to%20have%20ample%20space%2C%20efficiency%20and%20be%20cost-effective%2C%E2%80%9D%20Aravind%20Mani%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECracking%20the%20code%2C%20Aravind%2C%20along%20with%20his%20co-founder%2C%20Vipin%20George%2C%20made%20their%20electric%20two-wheeler%20with%2055%20litre%20of%20storage%20space%2C%20packing%20it%20with%20numerous%20qualities.%20Calling%20it%20the%20%E2%80%98SUV%20of%20Scooters%E2%80%99%2C%20Indie%20is%20an%20electric%20two-wheeler%20built%20under%20River.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20recently%20raised%20an%20investment%20of%20%2440%20million%20(Rs%20335%20crore)%20globally%20in%20an%20oversubscribed%20Series%20A%20and%20Series%20B%20round%20(second%20round%20of%20funding).%20Interestingly%2C%20Yamaha%20Motor%20Company%20and%20UAE%20automotive%20giant%2C%20Al-Futtaim%2C%20are%20among%20its%20top%20investors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFor%20the%20youth%20of%20the%20country%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECalling%20their%20partnership%20a%20perfect%20match%2C%20Aravind%20explains%20how%20their%20work%20at%20the%20startup%20is%20divided.%20%E2%80%9CVipin%20is%20a%20hardcore%20automobile%20guy%20and%20I%20know%20how%20to%20sell%20things.%20The%20combination%20is%20perfect%20and%20we%20both%20handle%20our%20respective%20areas%20of%20expertise%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20the%20co-founders%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F332097%2Fkerala-sustainable-home-disaster-resistant-ecofriendly-lgsf-technology%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20are%20from%20Kerala%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20met%20through%20a%20common%20company%20whe