to%20help%20other%20small%20businesses%20thrive%20with%20the%20right%20transportation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20utility%2C%20what%20they%20wanted%20to%20focus%20on%20as%20a%20company%20was%20the%20design.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FEV-5-1710756910.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Vipin%20George%20and%20Arvind%20Mani%2C%20founders%20of%20River.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FEV-5-1710756910.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FEV-5-1710756910-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FEV-5-1710756910-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FEV-5-1710756910-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FEV-5-1710756910-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-345055%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EVipin%20George%20and%20Aravind%20Mani%2C%20founders%20of%20River.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20India%2C%20we%20noticed%20that%20if%20something%20is%20high%20in%20utility%2C%20then%20its%20design%20is%20neglected.%20However%2C%20since%20we%20want%20to%20appeal%20to%20the%20youth%2C%20we%20want%20to%20give%20them%20the%20best%20design%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20youth%20knows%20what%20they%20want%20from%20the%20vehicle%20but%20also%20they%20want%20it%20to%20have%20some%20personality.%20So%20this%20became%20our%20driving%20force%2C%20we%20combine%20utility%20with%20design%20to%20create%20a%20product%20that%20is%20eco-friendly%20and%20suits%20our%20users.%20Just%20as%20a%20farmer%20drives%20h