%20600%20hectares%20of%20forest%20land%20was%20recovered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20sat%20down%20with%20the%2034-year-old%20to%20understand%20what%20goes%20into%20working%20as%20a%20forest%20officer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhere%20tigers%20were%20killed%20for%20fun%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHailing%20from%20Jaipur%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20Jain%20pursued%20civil%20engineering%20at%20IIT-Roorkee%20and%20cracked%20the%20UPSC%20exam%20to%20become%20an%20IFS%20officer%20in%202017.%20After%20two%20years%20of%20training%2C%20he%20was%20allotted%20the%20Chhattisgarh%20cadre%2C%20and%20in%20February%202022%2C%20he%20joined%20Udanti-Sitanadi%20Tiger%20Reserve%20as%20a%20deputy%20director.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharing%20its%20boundary%20with%20Odisha%2C%20the%20Udanti-Sitanadi%20tiger%20reserve%20is%20known%20for%20its%20rich%20vegetation%20and%20forest%20cover%20of%20sal%2C%20teak%2C%20and%20bamboo%20trees.%20It%20is%20also%20home%20to%20a%20diverse%20fauna%2C%20including%20leopards%2C%20wild%20buffaloes%2C%20tigers%2C%20hyenas%2C%20elephants%2C%20bears%2C%20pangolins%2C%20and%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20joining%20the%20tiger%20reserve%2C%20Jain%20observed%20a%20lack%20of%20awareness%20of%20wildlife%20and%20forest%20conservation%20among%20the%20local%20people.%20%E2%80%9CAs%20the%20area%20is%20Naxal-affected%2C%20forest%20officials%20would%20fear%20going%20for%20patrolling.%20This%20patrolling%20gap%20led%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F203827%2Fifs-hero-india-woman-forest-encroach-jungle-mafia-forests-real-hero-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erise%20in%20encroachment%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20poaching%20cases.%20People%20would%20cut%20down%20trees%20to%20build%20their%20establishments%20in%20animal%20habitats%20while%20poachers%20fanned%20the%20illegal%20wildlife%20trade%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5